          "uuid": "e19b497a-45c9-4fa0-ab63-2186c33d1bc5",
          "text": "Over the year to 31 December 2019, the Trustees and the Company have not taken any formal decisions over the process. The calculation of the allowance as a proportion of the liabilities included within the IAS 19 figures is therefore unchanged. As a result of changes in market conditions, the allowance is now \u00a33.2 million. The difference has been charged to profit and loss account reserves during the year as an experience gain/loss.",
